INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('35', '公开亮相！Shimano正式发布S-Phyre人身装备', 'Shimano,S-Phyre,人身装备', ' 2016年，Shimano发布了S-Phyre概念的性能锁鞋，《旋钮终于来了！Shimano发布新款S-PHYRE公路、越野锁鞋》中也能看到Shimano开发S-Phyre系列人身装备的行动。', 'Shimano', '20171111\\186fd7c1000cf78060badefba819d68d.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366844910064.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">2016年，Shimano发布了S-Phyre概念的性能锁鞋，<a href=\"http://www.biketo.com/product/29752.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"《旋钮终于来了！Shimano发布新款S-PHYRE公路、越野锁鞋》\" textvalue=\"《旋钮终于来了！Shimano发布新款S-PHYRE公路、越野锁鞋》\" style=\"cursor: pointer; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">《旋钮终于来了！Shimano发布新款S-PHYRE公路、越野锁鞋》</a>中也能看到Shimano开发S-Phyre系列人身装备的行动。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366845123138.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"218\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">在2017年，Shimano扩大S-Phyre概念，发布了相关的人身装备。世巡赛车队LottoNL-Jumbo荷兰乐透车队将在2017赛季使用S-Phyre定制服装和锁鞋。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366845714630.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">功率是每个职业车手都必须面对的问题，奋力骑行已经足够艰苦，骑手不应该再为空气阻力、摩擦或过热这些物理因素而损失能量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366846790008.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Shimano称，<span style=\"text-align: center;\">S-Phyre</span>的设计目标在于通过先进的科技限制这些损失，将联动及运动原理应用于自行车、身体与肌肉运动这一完整的系统之间。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">S-Phyre</span>的设计专门为了减少在人身装备上的功率损失。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366847423492.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Shimano包括骑行服上衣、背带骑行裤、连体骑行服、手套、袜子等产品在内的S-Phyre装备，设计均结合了专业车手的知识，旨在最大限度地提高服装和皮肤之间的接触效率，帮助骑手的表现更上层楼。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366848408050.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">S-Phyre骑行服上装和背带骑行短裤：骑行服上衣最大的特点是肩膀部位的无缝设计，3D结构减少肩部褶皱，Shimano的标志在黑色、黄色骑行服上都非常低调。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366848540161.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" title=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" alt=\"Shimano,骑行服,sphyre,锁鞋,手套,袜子,短袖,长袖\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">S-Phyre背带骑行裤的亮点是使用了减震的翼型麂皮垫裆设计。</p><p><br/></p>', '4', '0', '0', '1510366926', '69');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('42', '雾霾！雨雪！天气太冷！不想出去骑车怎么办？', '雾霾,雨雪,单车,装备', ' 骑行爱好者们都喜欢走出门外享受骑行，那感觉自由自在无拘无束，如小鸟一般翱翔在广阔的天地，然而骑行台，对很多人来说是枯燥的，无聊的，但它却是雨雪天，冬天，雾霾天不能出门骑车的最佳伴友。', '骑行圈', '20171116\\c49fb482bd5ed9f74cea4b6cfe1c57b0.jpg', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 102, 255); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; text-decoration-line: none !important;\">骑行</a>爱好者们都喜欢走出门外享受骑行，那感觉自由自在无拘无束，如小鸟一般翱翔在广阔的天地，然而骑行台，对很多人来说是枯燥的，无聊的，但它却是雨雪天，冬天，雾霾天不能出门骑车的最佳伴友。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">为什么要使用骑</strong><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">行台？</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">训练需要</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　骑行台的训练能更有针对性，也不是每天都有大把时间可以外出骑行，骑行台可以提供更稳定的环境，不需要考虑道路等干扰因素。也不用担心摔车的受伤，每天抽出一两个小时就可以骑上几十公里，甚至可以一边骑车一边看电视，无形中提高训练效率。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764181310607.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 800px; margin: 5px 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">天气因素</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　无论职业车手还是一般的爱好者，都有越来越多的人转向了室内骑行台的训练。大多数的原因会是因为天气，比如现在进入了冬天，北方室外的温度低了，还有下雨，还有更糟糕的雾霾。一般的车友骑车锻炼是为了健康，但如果糟糕的环境下骑行，比如着凉，比如雾霾，这样就得不偿失了，骑行反而会让身体更不健康。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764181195800.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 800px; margin: 5px 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">效率考量</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　骑行台可以让你的训练更节约时间。比如晚上回来晚了，无法参加夜骑；比如城市太大了，花在路上的时间还比上强度骑行的时间长，而正常的工作日则没那么多的时间花在这，而骑行台就成了较高效的选择。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764181984802.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 800px; margin: 5px 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">滚筒骑行台还是固定骑行台？</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　就像很多人会纠结<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/article-2729-1.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 102, 255); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; text-decoration-line: none !important;\">shimano</a>还是<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/article-2730-1.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 102, 255); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; text-decoration-line: none !important;\">sram</a>一样，滚筒还是固定骑行台的选择对于没接触过的车友，也是个艰难的选择。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764182423706.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 800px; margin: 5px 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">上图为滚筒骑行台</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　两种骑行台的使用都比较方便，一般来说，滚筒的骑行台除了可以锻炼你的体能外，还能提高你的骑行技术，而固定的骑行台则更注重高强度的训练。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　但固定骑行台在骑行时不需要去保持平衡，可以解放双手，甚至一心多用，看视频，刷手机都可以。而滚筒骑行台则需要完全集中注意力来骑行，否则有受伤的可能。小编建议，对于日常体能训练或者减肥的需求来讲，固定骑行台更适合一些。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">骑行台的使用</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　对于使用，<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">首先必须的是使用光头胎，最好是1.5的光头胎，甚至1.25的，不用太贵，便宜的三十多块钱的即可</strong>，尤其是<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/shandiche/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 102, 255); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; text-decoration-line: none !important;\">山地车</a>，齿胎产生的噪音比较大，除非住一楼，不然在家里这么骑肯定会影响到别人的正常生活。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　对轮组则没什么要求，但如果<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">有条件多买一个后轮</strong>，方便随时更换就不用每次出去骑都要换外胎了。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　另外可以多<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">准备一个手机支架</strong>，方便一般骑行一般看手机视频，以免不那么枯燥。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　最后，建议<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">在地上铺一个垫子</strong>，以减少震动，减小共振产生的噪音。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">小编感受：</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">　　当骑行成为你生活的一种习惯，你会发现。一有空闲时间，不去碰下车子。心里空唠唠的，尤其到了冬天，外面雾霾又大，就没有心情再出去闲逛了，这时候家里有一部骑行台，解决了生活的所有烦恼。也许这个冬天，你也需要来一台骑行台。</p>', '0', '0', '1', '1510764195', '68');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('43', '有些路，一生一次——而立之前，送自己一个丙察察', '', ' 有这么一条路，当人们谈论起来时，往往不是风景美不美，也不是道路是否泥泞难行、崎岖不堪，甚至还有很多人并不知道有这么一条路存在。初识这条路便是——丙察察', '骑行圈', '20171116\\a24fbef5eb16bd1617e3eaaa71a42593.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\">有这么一条路，当人们谈论起来时，往往不是风景美不美，也不是道路是否泥泞难行、崎岖不堪，甚至还有很多人并不知道有这么一条路存在。初识这条路便是在刚开始<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue;\">骑行</a>时骑行圈里的一个帖子，如同打开了一扇新世界的大门，我为之癫狂。我几乎花了一整年的时间去搜寻征服它的攻略（痴痴地翻阅一篇又一篇的游记、尽可能的搜寻穿越的骑友询问注意事项），第一次想征服它是在2014年，我做好了所有的准备，却在临行前与它擦肩而过。它有很多响亮的名字：滇藏新通道、滇藏西线、第八条进藏通道、最后的进藏路。在众多的名字中，我独爱那最原始的叫法——丙察察，始于云南省贡山独龙族怒族自治县丙中洛镇，经<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/gotibet/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue;\">西藏</a>自治区察隅县察瓦龙乡，直至西藏自治区察隅县的一条四级简易公路。人们谈论到它，最多的话语便是“这条路通不通？”拖延了三年，也是丙察察修路三年即将期满之时，我终于踏上了征程。三年后的丙察察，是否能够顺利通过，还是会因塌方不通改走丙察左，一切都是未知。带着所有的期待，我上路了。</span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225227\" aid=\"225227\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764767164764.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103048guj5nee2w965jncv.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103048guj5nee2w965jncv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"627\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>丙察察线示意图（红色为丙察线，蓝色为察察线：察瓦龙经目巴木孔至目若非图中所示）</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225226\" aid=\"225226\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764770147857.jpeg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103047isf5rkjm0kwf5fom.jpeg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103047isf5rkjm0kwf5fom.jpeg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>沙布村下的烂路，丙察察线的缩影</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225225\" aid=\"225225\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764771841400.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103046rnjobwnnzvp6smoz.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/29/103046rnjobwnnzvp6smoz.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>通向齐马拉山口的最初的简易公路，现已改道</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228496\" aid=\"228496\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764771882110.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012622wwsi7m2gw7117m2i.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012622wwsi7m2gw7117m2i.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>把我带上这条路的一句话</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228499\" aid=\"228499\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764772125457.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012724arasnwnnpwifnbpg.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012724arasnwnnpwifnbpg.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>大流沙</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228500\" aid=\"228500\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764772395660.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012754dbr11137hb23b1u9.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012754dbr11137hb23b1u9.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>每个行者大概都有一张类似的照片</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228501\" aid=\"228501\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764772235687.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012813ub3nqjjba46nh4lj.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012813ub3nqjjba46nh4lj.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>DONE</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228502\" aid=\"228502\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764773657257.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012902rn15p5m456a142oh.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012902rn15p5m456a142oh.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"725\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p>全程3D记录</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_228498\" aid=\"228498\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171116/1510764773890838.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012722qburcu1ititcuewx.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201710/28/012722qburcu1ititcuewx.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><span style=\"font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\">为了这次旅行，请了足够长的假。不必像那些单单为了突破丙察的行者那样把车带到贡山开启穿越之行。我把这次旅行分割成了三段，也算是完成梦想的三部曲。在这不长不短的骑行生涯里，我有很多路想要去骑，比如独库公路、壁挂公路。年近三十，事业、家庭等迫在眉睫之事是不允许我再跑到遥远的新疆去赴一趟充满不确定因素的约定。权衡再三，决定把寻找坚毅、果敢的自己的旅行放在了丙察察。</span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 这段圆梦之旅共圆了三个梦：怒江大峡谷骑行、穿越丙察察、单车带我到布宫。游记也可大致的分割为四个篇章。本想换个不同的方式来记录，苦于文字功底薄弱，还是回归熟悉的日记视角来记录这生命中不可多得的精彩吧。</span></span></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510764776', '70');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('34', '碳纤维死飞车 一辆来自外太空的自行车', '碳纤维,死飞车,科幻,外太空', '  Velonia 制造的 Viks是一个有固定齿轮的自行车，它有着惊人的美感，许多媒体都评价，它是一辆来自外太空的自行车。Viks完全用不锈钢管制作，配有两个相同形状的圆柱框架来固定车身。现在，该公司又在Viks的基础上，为我们带来了一辆全新的自行车Viks Carbon，这是一个更加轻盈的版本。', '威锋网', '20171111\\dd9dac9ca29dbe9f8e1787836e341996.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366973396606.jpg\" data-width=\"818\" data-height=\"544\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">自行车自被发明以来，永远都<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">不</span>是过时的交通工具。不管从材质，造型设计，功能等方面来说，自行车一直都紧随着时代发展的脚步，不断提升自己，在全世界范围内，一直存在着许许多多的自行车爱好者。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366974631896.jpg\" data-width=\"818\" data-height=\"544\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Velonia 制造的 Viks是一个有固定齿轮的自行车，它有着惊人的美感，许多媒体都评价，它是一辆来自外太空的自行车。Viks完全用不锈钢管制作，配有两个相同形状的圆柱框架来固定车身。现在，该公司又在Viks的基础上，为我们带来了一辆全新的自行车Viks Carbon，这是一个更加轻盈的版本。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366974431152.jpg\" data-width=\"682\" data-height=\"1024\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"503\" height=\"750\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Velonia与所有的自行车爱好者一样，都希望将最新的科技技术应用到自行车上。这次他们就为自行车带来了碳纤维框架。Viks carbon的碳纤维框架车身重达四公斤，而它的前任Viks采用不锈钢制成的车身框架重量为7公斤。 Viks Carbon的设备非常齐全，要知道 Viks利用了赛车风格的摩托车元素和经典的流线型美学来进行设计的，作为继任者，Viks Carbon自然也吸取了Viks所有的优点，而且还做得更加出色。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366974196716.jpg\" data-width=\"818\" data-height=\"544\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Viks Carbon车身所使用的碳管都由斯洛文尼亚碳复合材料建造公司所制造的，该公司希望车友可以骑着Viks Carbon飞驰一辈子。Viks Carbon车身上还包括不锈钢接头，不锈钢脚踏板，Aerospoke碳纤维轮组，每一个骑行习惯不一样的自行车车手都可以根据自身特点对其进行定制。<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">独特的Viks Carbon已经在<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">2015</span>欧洲自行车展</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">上与我们见面。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366975174682.jpg\" data-width=\"818\" data-height=\"544\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">现在越来越多的上班族已经放弃汽车，选择使用自行车作为自己的代步工具了，这样不仅可以减少环境污染，减轻城市的压力，而且对于自己的身体也是有着万般的好处的，当然，骑自行车我们还可以避免抢占车位的烦恼。不过需要注意的是，Viks Carbon可是一辆”死飞“，如果你觉得驾驭不了，或者出于安全性考虑，我们还是选择带刹车的自行车比较稳妥。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510366975204895.jpg\" data-width=\"818\" data-height=\"544\" title=\"Viks Carbon\" alt=\"Viks Carbon\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">Viks carbon的前任Viks的售价为 1200 多欧元，不知道这款同样来自“外太空”的自行车，售价会是多少呢？</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510366757', '65');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('33', '700BIKE复古骑行：钢铁森林里的一股优雅气息', '复古,骑行,变装,中世纪', '  今年，700Bike复古骑行系列活动已经覆盖到成都和广州，集结了越来越多的复古潮派人士，为这个充满后现代主义和钢铁森林的城市带来一股清新的优雅气息。', 'BIKETO（Max）', '20171111\\7dafe82f5b25c5d83efcefc383f2fff6.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">身处在一线城市，总能见识到许多新鲜的事情。比如近两年兴起了骑行之风，可当大部分人还沉浸在换零件换骑行服，刷街冲山练腿的进竞速练计划里时，一群会玩的城里人们却已悄然开始追求另一种骑行乐趣。他们完全不纠结于要山地还是公路，铝架还是碳架，上锁还是不上锁。他们穿着西装皮鞋，或长裙高跟鞋，蓄着小胡子或画着精致的妆容，优雅地踩着车迎面而来。就像是一群从中世纪穿越而来的绅士与淑女。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">你猜到他们在干什么了吗？没错，这就是由700Bike兴起的复古变装骑行系列活动。它展示了“崇尚经典文化，希望将时光的留影记录于心”的生活态度，用复古变装的骑行方式来表达“保持精致，踏向美好”的生活愿望。而Max在开篇里描述的，就是复古骑行活动广州站的景象。这是活动的第四站，也是最后一站。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">复古骑行也叫Vintage Ride，起源于英国伦敦，要求参与者必须穿着充满传统英伦风格的复古装束，骑上自己的复古自行车，在每年的春天沿着伦敦中心城区骑行，这个始于2009年的活动很快便风靡全球。2013年9月20日，由潮流单车网站700Bike携手优质生活杂志《城市画报》，继北京之后，首次将复古骑行引入了摩登上海。到今年，700Bike复古骑行系列活动已经覆盖到成都和广州，集结了越来越多的复古潮派人士，为这个充满后现代主义和钢铁森林的城市带来一股清新的优雅气息。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/37949d12879bdc7ad684ffa31eb0d28c.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">前一周广州还陆续下了5天雨，直到这两天周末开始放晴，特别是今天还出了太阳。阳光透过层层叠叠的树叶洒下来，让所有人都自带了美颜效果。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/6742f4229bf9c5c1a7afdc7c461c510e.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">福利放送第一弹：签到处的一众美女们。Max也表示很惊喜，很少有活动能见到如此多漂亮的妹子。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/f7ca3e7568a59bc25a60cd7932f50978.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">签到即送礼包一个，里面有一套精致的明信片和活动海报等礼品，让人爱不释手。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/fc8bd7eb4454595b68b95a2a9bf5a43d.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"963\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">现场布置得十分用心，每一样物件都散发着浓浓的Vintage气息。Max表示真想把它们都搬回家。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/a033164081017701f37a364d282b8fa8.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">复古的一家三口，妈妈的装扮完完全全就是Max心目中的Vintage范儿。可惜小朋友害羞不肯露脸拍照。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/a0d836e38a431711a974139acd4e2a7e.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"963\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">福利放送第二弹：我知道你们就喜欢看美女，现在让你一次看个够。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/a8c170d4cec7cf4c895a0f1318b974c8.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"642\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">美女配帅哥，淑女配绅士，赏心又悦目。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/6b8ce38356ce3a212606f2defb0860ed.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"320\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">除了有好看的，还有好吃的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/bf95028ad0e067ea4e4f987c780fceb6.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">在各种凹造型停不下来的时候，复古大会也正式开始。首先由赞助商之一Clarance Wong周总为大家示范如何打领带。因为打领带在粤语里称为“打tai”，所以现场主持人每说到这个词时总让人一阵凌乱。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/f1e6d1f086338cbc8dada744ec08fe1f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"639\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">睁大眼睛认真看，一会就是上台爆人品的时候了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/44ad1a1608061b767c8b874cf19b8a3c.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"320\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">最终这位长腿偶吧在partner的帮助下打出了完美的领带，除了获得奖品之外还和美女评委合影一张。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/019484b366a45ea5af6e4075108e7655.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"320\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">既然今天大家都花费了好一番心思打扮来此，又怎能不用一场show来好好展示呢？不过带了“特别道具（小狗）”上场的，可真是辛苦了主持人，不过谁叫他自己跟妹子说“你负责扮美，我来给你遛狗”呢？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/32cc7c7d940d5476a2fa3cd5bf6ddf88.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">由于复古走秀的优胜者可以得到700Bike整车一辆，而名额却只有两名，男女各一名，由评委加观众投票得出，所以上台走秀的选手都想方设法展示自己独特的一面来拉票。这位帅哥平时就是个死飞爱好者，一上了台更是耍得停不下来。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/a0eb7987bb0def8a0fc0b9008b716fa9.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">主持人笑说这位的耳朵特别像“谢耳朵”（美剧《生活大爆炸》主演之一）。仔细看他脖子上的眼镜也是个小亮点哦。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/d0f6170067c51c449fc5fcad83582696.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">又一位死飞爱好者上台，比上一位玩的更激烈。这位帅哥说他从很小的时候就喜欢骑车，到大学接触到死飞后，开始迈入发烧友阶段，平花是他最拿手的把式。甚至还影响到上图的“谢耳朵”，把他带入了骑行界。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/cd172a26229a97c73c8dd4cc076426b9.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">本场最雍容华贵的选手，上台时却是推着车一步一跳的活泼软妹子，跟这身貂皮贵妇风形成了强烈反差，立马收获台下评委“好赞”卡一张。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/26bb44d802c3a6b27356fb692778a08f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">制服诱惑之上世纪40年代的苏联女兵军装风。有没有让你轻轻吟起《喀秋莎》和回想起《这里的黎明静悄悄》？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/849e59e6c0ce67c42239c7371288ccf2.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">可爱的双生姐妹花。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/1ab3530cfcd5afe49e12e0b9c868a0f9.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">本场show的赢家之一——复古的老派绅士男神。有种吴秀波的感觉。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/b45383e45bdab9dd12d34ec8878a1c4c.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"639\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/23e91c90fc6b67237571ceac5be3a397.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"639\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/7a964111b0917abcf4d731f1d693f894.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"639\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">结束了复古走秀，骑行便正式开始。短短的三公里路线虽然不长，但足够赚人眼球，绝对是今天广州城里最亮眼的风景线之一。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/b711d7ec3104c38e024e04374397f61d.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"642\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">折返回来之后可以去创意园内的哲品休息喝茶，等待六点开始After Party。在这之前，当然是各种拍照合影留恋这美美的一刻了。毕竟今晚一过就要穿越回现代了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/0494b0565629c5a738a2ebe16f687a43.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">看着其他站的视频，大家也在静静地回味着今天的活动。虽然广州站的规模没有北京上海那么大，但这样反而展示了一种小而美的景象，所有的精致细节都可以放大让人静静品味。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2016-01-18/bcc03aeeaee4cfff54395d286e352d8c.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"639\" title=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" alt=\"700Bike复古骑行活动\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">你是不是已经准备好参加明年的活动了呢？</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510366216', '66');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('37', '做一家特别的车店：昆山乐游家单车生活馆探访', '单车生活,单车生活馆,车店', '  姚建峰（Ricky）认为“现在如果还是以直白的方式去推广自行车，效果是不如人意的。”因此他把车店作为单车文化生活馆，命名为乐游家bikecafe，并将其作为推广单车文化的平台。', '凌子', '20171111\\5f3e22a3e5d115cc92a07a52dd3894d6.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">姚建峰在自行车行业少说也呆了十来年，呆过工厂，跑过销售，做过外贸，现在自己在昆山开了家车店。其实这样的人生轨迹在这个行业应该一抓一撮，为什么今天的话题非得是他？主要还在于他那个特别的店。以下就跟随那个前段时间上江苏的小编去看看吧，顺便看看这个车店能不能满足你对于一家有意思的车店的全部幻想。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/135180ff3a44020417ea93c05f88b290.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"600\" title=\"乐游家\" alt=\"乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/eb652f3a409d38f690671ffe802507de.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"534\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" line-height:=\"\">▲<span style=\"line-height: 34px; font-size: 16px;\">乐游家被定义为自行车·咖啡·生活馆</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">姚建峰（Ricky）认为“现在如果还是以直白的方式去推广自行车，效果是不如人意的。”因此他把车店作为单车文化生活馆，命名为乐游家bikecafe，并将其作为推广单车文化的平台。然而一开始很多人都不理解他开的店到底是做什么的。咖啡厅吗？甚至他开业的时候业内人造访时还不敢保证这个位于昆山金鹰商业街的车店能活过行业寒冬，一年后当我们跟业界谈起乐游家，有些前辈却说道，“也许以后这种店活得更好”，捷安特、美利达的管理层也曾到店观摩，可见这个店在本地还是小有名气。而它从开业至今也已实现小有盈余。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/e5b728c7c77e1aaa307a1e430904daf9.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"534\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" line-height:=\"\">▲<span style=\"line-height: 34px; font-size: 16px;\">店内的装修也是Ricky亲自设计的</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/a20e87c3a44ee4e4b3624cdce4cb5e50.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"1067\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" width=\"800\" height=\"1067\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" line-height:=\"\">▲<span style=\"line-height: 34px; font-size: 16px;\">店里只有一个服务员，他既要当服务员，又要煮咖啡调饮料</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/59428b535967a39b2defb5bbf0f069d2.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"533\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" line-height:=\"\">▲自己研磨咖啡豆，我们当然也喝了一杯</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/d9d0de5c7df9fc7a1189d5b348f0ec37.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"533\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/industry/business/2016-10-25/030710d8c985f04634d5d8b5d6e8f718.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"340\" title=\"昆山乐游家\" alt=\"昆山乐游家\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" line-height:=\"\">▲<span style=\"line-height: 34px; font-size: 16px;\">店内舒服的角落，在这里喝上一杯咖啡跟三两好友谈谈心</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '1', '1510367280', '70');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('38', '摩拜完成超6亿美元E轮融资 创共享单车行业单笔融资最高纪录', '摩拜,融资,共享单车', ' 今天（6月16日），全球智能共享单车行业首创者摩拜单车宣布完成一笔超过6亿美元的新一轮融资，创下共享单车行业单笔融资最高纪录。本轮融资由腾讯领投，新引入的战略和财务投资者包括工银国际、交银国际、Farallon Capital等重磅投资人；TPG、红杉中国、高瓴资本等多家现有股东继续增持跟投。', ' 美骑网', '20171111\\1feb1e2adfc70769c10ce4116686fbcb.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">今天（6月16日）<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">，全球智能共享单车行业首创者摩拜单车宣布完成一笔超过6亿美元的新一轮融资，创下共享单车行业单笔融资最高纪录。本轮融资由腾讯领投，新引入的战略和财务投资者包括工银国际、交银国际、Farallon Capital等重磅投资人；TPG、红杉中国、高瓴资本等多家现有股东继续增持跟投。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510367363594696.jpg\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"600\" title=\"摩拜完成超6亿美元E轮融资 创共享单车行业单笔融资最高纪录\" alt=\"摩拜完成超6亿美元E轮融资 创共享单车行业单笔融资最高纪录\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">2016年4月摩拜单车在上海投入运营，此后迅速扩展至北京、广州、深圳、成都、天津、新加坡等城市。近日登陆英国曼彻斯特和索尔福德两市后，其在全球布局城市突破100座，运营车辆超过500万辆，日订单量最高超过2500万，注册用户超过1亿，是全球最大的智能共享单车平台和互联网出行平台。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">摩拜单车联合创始人兼CEO王晓峰称，新一轮融资将助力摩拜单车国际化进程，计划年底服务全球200座城市；此外摩拜还将携手全球领先物联网合作伙伴，推动移动物联网技术的进步和实景应用；另外还将在人工智能、智能硬件等领域加速战略布局和技术创新。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">摩拜每一辆单车均独家配备“北斗+GPS+格洛纳斯”多模卫星定位芯片和物联网芯片，在行业独家打造了全球无缝连接的移动物联网系统，首次实现NB-IoT物联网技术的实景应用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">腾讯继C轮投资、D轮领投摩拜单车后，再一次领投摩拜。此外双方还在多个层面上展开合作，包括摩拜单车首批入驻微信“小程序”、入驻微信钱包“九宫格”等。腾讯董事会主席兼首席执行官马化腾表示，腾讯将继续开放包括微信在内的核心资源，为摩拜单车持续提供成长动能，助力摩拜单车的创新和业务扩张。分析人士认为，摩拜单车此轮融资将加速行业优势资源向头部企业靠拢。</p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">名词解释：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">“北斗+GPS+格洛纳斯”多模卫星定位：</span>三者都位列全球四大卫星导航系统。北斗是中国的系统，GPS是美国陆海空三军联合研制的系统，<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">格洛纳斯是俄罗斯的系统。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">NB-IoT物联网技术：</span>LPWA (Low Power Wide Area) 是有低带宽、低功耗、远距离通信、广覆盖、海量连接要求的物联网应用，是适合由运营商部署的一种物联网技术，包括 NB-IOT、LoRa、Sigfox 等技术。其中，NB-IOT是由华为主导，具有覆盖广（能覆盖到地下）、电池寿命长（超过十年）、成本低（每个模块不足 5 美元）、容量大（单个小区能支持 10 万连接）四大能力。<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"></span></p><hr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">编辑评论：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">从去年运营至今，共享单车被预言存在的问题已接二连三地暴露，甚至惹上过贪腐丑闻，不少媒体毫不客气地“唱衰”共享单车，为它们的消亡倒计时。因共享单车占道影响市民出行，媒体文章的读者评论区总有希望共享单车消失的声音。这样的舆论走向却不影响融资推进的步伐。自行车业内不少整车厂表示近来共享单车的订单开始减少，怀疑共享单车企业烧融资已烧得差不多，对资金会有进一步需求。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">据《第一财经》此前报道，ofo也正以30亿美元的估值寻求新一轮融资，这笔融资的金额大概是5亿美元，该消息也得到了一位某投资机构的知情人士的证实。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">对于增持跟投的风投而言，不会让自己已经投了大笔资金的项目死在手里，既然套现不了，就要继续让它的估值涨上去，推高估值再找机会套现。这与乐视名声愈走愈下却依然有投资者愿意跟投的思路是相似的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">值得留意的是，新引入的投资机构中有财务投资者，说明他们相信摩拜是有盈利能力的，希望未来能从利润中获得分红。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510367389', '71');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('39', '海口首届复古骑行 以优雅姿态致敬经典', '海口,复古骑行,优雅,经典', '   近千名来自省内外的复古骑行爱好者，身着民国风情的复古盛装，汇集海口骑楼老街，形成一道别具一格的风景。老街以其鲜明的建筑特色，厚重的文化背景，无疑成就了一次独特的复古骑行盛宴。', 'BIKETO（凌子）', '20171111\\bc14adae5b9ecf2836688ee9dd10621c.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">很多骑行爱好者会把环海南岛列入人生的环岛计划，可见海南岛的骑行氛围之浓烈，当地的骑行族越来越庞大，活动愈加丰富。自行车从代步工具逐步蜕变成休闲娱乐用品。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">12月13日，海南迎来了主题为“回味优雅，时光传骑”的首次复古骑行活动。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">近千名来自省内外的复古骑行爱好者，身着民国风情的复古盛装，汇集海口骑楼老街，形成一道别具一格的风景。老街以其鲜明的建筑特色，厚重的文化背景，无疑成就了一次独特的复古骑行盛宴。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">活动内容特别的丰富多彩，有才艺演出、复古服装秀、单车秀、模仿秀、骑楼•书香+咖啡•时光复古展演场景，有复古骑行巡游骑楼老街，有骑楼美食汇，骑楼文化讲座等。活动现场不仅有天涯骑驴俱乐部提供的价值近十万元的奖品，更有捷安特海南赞助百辆全新的莫曼顿咖啡休闲现代复古单车，由复古骑行爱好者们免费骑乘体验。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/334754bdec7d6e464b56b361edafaf3f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"640\" title=\"海口复古骑行-骑楼老街\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-骑楼老街\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">这次活动由海南天涯骑驴发起，俱乐部严春江会长说：“复古骑行宣扬的不仅是一种服装上的品味和爱好，还是一种生活方式。现代人的生活节奏快，生活方式也不尽环保，着装上也越来越缺乏含蓄和经典的美感。我们希望用复古骑行的方式传达爱护家园、倡导低碳生活理念，同时也向那个大街小巷遍布自行车的美好年代致敬。”上午十一点严会长已经开始在现场指导，海口本地书法家特地为此活动题字。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/88d26c87e690f79079d177271a03c2ec.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-楚男\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-楚男\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">深圳体育康复中心赛务部主任楚南老师总是一脸严肃，然而他是一个极度幽默的人，他曾多次担任大型赛事及户外活动的后勤保障。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/4257560c9cd063af9efecb362d127c7f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-黑人帮\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-黑人帮\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">男人帮，你应该听楚男老师讲一些笑话，一天都会有好心情。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/68bfcddf631d2773d0d15470121f2d40.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"659\" title=\"海口复古骑行-严会长\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-严会长\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">天涯骑驴俱乐部建立时间由来已久，人员配置相当齐全，很多事情不再需要严总亲力亲为，他们戏称她为太后。“太后”穿起旗袍还是很有范~<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/8d6c654a6bcc6e703f80e805d9689565.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"657\" title=\"海口复古骑行-母女\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-母女\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">禅姐是多个户外骑行活动的策划者，本次活动她也有份参谋，她表示想尝试做一些精致但挖掘深层意义的活动，复古骑行和单车成人礼都是尝试，复古骑行从想法提出到执行耗费大半年时间。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/5fff9d88f225f3d0137ab2c4894b1404.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"693\" title=\"海口复古骑行-美女们\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-美女们\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">骑遇骑楼老街 优雅致敬经典</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/fb1d51e8ea75c3ff4904baa4d3e525e5.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"632\" title=\"海口复古骑行-花\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-花\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">带着花一样的心情来参加这场热闹的聚会</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/bfb8beb31ad1232658a393e77bd39f11.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"676\" title=\"海口复古骑行-复古单车\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-复古单车\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">不知道是谁的收藏品？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/42e1906f6151361f26e585cc453e5275.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"619\" title=\"海口复古骑行-女学生\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-女学生\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">重返少女时代</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/6ee2f6de38fcb9aea2d46f175034e250.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-女士\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-女士\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/5d0516e08ff31fa2f8e818ef136f024f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"723\" title=\"骑友.jpg\" alt=\"骑友.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">这位骑友这辆买菜车还是90年代日本普利司通产的（左）；花车上的美女并不是车友，为了参加今天的活动特地买了旗袍（右）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/f500be1e01a53abf3d3fadf3265b3778.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-女士2\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-女士2\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">当地的骑行爱好者们踊跃参与</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/ec3c3443af7de635687a3b137f97a4a8.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"630\" title=\"海口复古骑行-很酷的妹子\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-很酷的妹子\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">这位妹子也为这次出场做了好一阵功夫</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/ece829a2fcc564f1641963d9734f3131.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-女士3\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-女士3\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/fb43f68c58bbb9bdb699aad584fa4451.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"725\" title=\"撑伞美女.jpg\" alt=\"撑伞美女.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">女人的美也会随岁月而增长</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/30534f8489b4df03ec44f35b9251bf12.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-莫曼顿\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-莫曼顿\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">现场提供了莫曼顿城市车体验骑行，这个涂装很圣诞</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/42ac458a242dd28934e7c3af836e40e1.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"636\" title=\"海口复古骑行-骑行\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-骑行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">骑楼老街上一下子多了不少骑车的人，这一对单车上的情侣让我想起了父辈单车上的爱情，以下开始虐狗模式……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/ee64852bf23130735dc10af8f4aae369.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"713\" title=\"虐死单身汪.jpg\" alt=\"虐死单身汪.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">时尚的主持二人组，虐杀了多少菲林（左）；壁咚，来自香港的波波是个很逗的大叔，最是能哄人开心，对他来说现在衡量做不做一件事的标准是有没有意义。他跟女友dudu的爱情也可以拿出来当楷模。他称能给女友最大的浪漫就是说走就走的旅行，俩人经常一个心血来潮就四轮加两轮到处骑车。可能今晚突然说到重庆打火锅，明天小情侣就在重庆开涮。好吧，被壁咚的女生并不是他女友。因为他很能开玩笑。（右）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/837c4c501eecd37e9df5c28253525050.jpg\" data-width=\"959\" data-height=\"637\" title=\"大行\" alt=\"大行\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">波波带来的大行第一代，出于90年代，他是个小径车迷，家里已经收藏了三十多台。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/e41eafe695c24bbc2f5b92232a99321b.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"647\" title=\"海口复古骑行-单身汪\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-单身汪\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">真的是虐狗，人类玩得很开心的时候，单身汪被绑在一边眼巴巴看着别人……<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/44758c4c5365db5f794936214a047d0f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"648\" title=\"海口复古骑行-书法画作展览\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-书法画作展览\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">现场的书法和水墨画表演，这位年过七旬的老人笔力深厚<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/8402bf590f1ad11da4bafc60b92d2172.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"713\" title=\"复古骑行.jpg\" alt=\"复古骑行.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">禅姐的百变换装让人目不暇接<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/1799de847aea5de055648d350b1d0b38.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"615\" title=\"海口复古骑行-骑楼老街\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-骑楼老街\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">椰城自由骑俱乐部的成员大多已经退休，年纪最小五十出头，年长的已经七十有余，不服老的他们乐在其中。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/7af333fb0ebafaa5a23201aaa3cf21da.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"663\" title=\"鲜花与美人\" alt=\"鲜花与美人\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">鲜花与美人更配</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/fd4cc3365f43b540ef0a1184137357d0.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-62岁老人\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-62岁老人\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/67e92f4464362c0199510d0aa02d29d4.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"429\" title=\"宝刀未老.jpg\" alt=\"宝刀未老.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">这位带着孙女一起来玩的七十多岁大爷发型特别潮，身材保持得比年轻人还好，只身骑行川藏线，从海口骑往北京，他是俱乐部的代表人物。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/189f67380db7901027ed921733286f8b.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"734\" title=\"经典照.jpg\" alt=\"经典照.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">经典再现</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/fcaf294b669c19614e8b860a1555f65f.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-文艺汇演\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-文艺汇演\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">文艺汇演</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/4bdf861d7eebb9853ac22fa8a6a65705.jpg\" data-width=\"959\" data-height=\"668\" title=\"海口复古骑行-楚男老师演讲\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-楚男老师演讲\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">楚男老师扮演鲁迅演讲“运动不耍流氓”，他让现场参与者测算最高心率，并表示，比赛或者平时运动在自己的峰值范围内进行才安全。假设一个人安全心率是185，结果冲到200并且持续几十上百分钟，心脏和携氧能力都会跟不上，危险随之而来。他希望每一位运动者能为自己的健康负责。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/00af94679e7c6c4f21eaa537394fbfe1.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"638\" title=\"海口复古骑行-探戈\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-探戈\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">当熟悉的夜来香响起，台下也翩翩起舞</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/9985c079966687ff093ecaaa89a8fe01.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-再别康桥\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-再别康桥\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">海经院的学生代表朗诵再别康桥</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/1d87e8a3e5adea81e057ddcfbab65b1a.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-善舞\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-善舞\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">中国功夫</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/784f8aa8daa0a091e2080cad7fc25893.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"641\" title=\"海口复古骑行-现场书法\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-现场书法\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">海南本土歌手姚逊也是一位自行车爱好者，车龄半年多的他在骑行中受到启发创作了一首骑行的歌曲，每次唱起来总会想起以前的故事，每每热泪盈眶。书法家现场为“复古骑行题字”。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/activity/2015-12-14/7d32367f27bdd1b027e8974f0b006f12.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"635\" title=\"海口复古骑行-海口历史\" alt=\"海口复古骑行-海口历史\" style=\"border: 0px; margin-bottom: -10px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">讲座介绍海口的发展史以及骑楼老街的由来</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">活动结束了，早上临走的时候还前往海口捷安特总店拜访，工作人员还正忙于把活动的物品整理归位，感叹他们的辛苦，一位女士却淡然表示做的活动多，已经习惯了。略过活动本身，不仅是天涯骑驴俱乐部的工作人员，我们都应该感谢那些奋斗在各个城市为诸位骑友的周末生活添彩的活动组织者们。很多像婵姐这样的业余组织者周末忙完周一还要继续上班，大多数赶周五晚的飞机抵达目的地，活动结束之后又赶周一的早班当早鸟。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); line-height: 2; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">再来谈谈参加完活动的个人感受，这些年国内举办的复古骑行活动层出不穷，各具特色。但归结到一点，还是要好玩，让更多人一起来玩，而不仅仅是少数精英的游戏，更好的当然是提供给大众一个开眼界涨姿势的平台，让人们更深切感受到自行车的历史、精品、趣味性甚至车友的才华，我也不推崇“一统天下”，和而不同更有意思。海南的复古骑行最大特点是更加突出中国的传统，把国学、国画、书法等结合起来，可能大多数人只是报以欣赏，但艺术人把它们作为生命，这就值得我们好好尊重。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '1', '1510371417', '66');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('40', '昨日重现 Eroica复古骑行 不一样的豪车盛宴', 'Eroica,豪车盛宴,复古骑行 ', ' 2016年10月2日，当我们享受着难得的国庆假期，在意大利Chianti山区，七千多名车友也正在享受着他们的Eroica复古狂欢骑行。本次复古骑行设置了46km、75km、115km、135km和209km五个级别的终点，最后每个人都获得了一枚奖牌，享受了一盘意大利面，并承诺明年再聚。', 'Stephen Farrrand', '20171111\\cd5ad3c3dc95c1c265de0260dd0879be.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">2016年10月2日，当我们享受着难得的国庆假期，在意大利Chianti山区，七千多名车友也正在享受着他们的Eroica复古狂欢骑行，Eroica意大利语是“英雄”之意，车友们使用的车辆必需是1987年前生产钢管车，着装风格也力求与年代相符，这场盛会仿佛让时光倒流，把所有人带回1987年以前。本次复古骑行设置了46km、75km、115km、135km和209km五个级别的终点，最后每个人都获得了一枚奖牌，享受了一盘意大利面，并承诺明年再聚。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371506470947.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3262-1475577811669-iwoqowzabn5-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3262-1475577811669-iwoqowzabn5-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">来自埃塞克斯的四位车友在完成了115公里的赛程之后，向记者展示他们的自行车。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371507250183.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3263-1475577811675-40q9tyc7nnxa-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3263-1475577811675-40q9tyc7nnxa-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">▲优雅的香槟色BASSO</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371507663696.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3270-1475577811693-xdzjrynecenn-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3270-1475577811693-xdzjrynecenn-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Bianchi是Eroica的官方赞助商之一，结束了一天的赛程，两辆Bianchi在一起相互依偎。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371507426330.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3272-1475577811696-c9e1mfohdble-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3272-1475577811696-c9e1mfohdble-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">▲Bianchi的大名被细致地雕刻在后上叉上<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371508596679.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3266-1475577811683-1vk3m624vtjxr-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3266-1475577811683-1vk3m624vtjxr-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">自行车品牌Tommasini来自沿海小镇Grosseto。上图中的这辆橙色的自行车是Tommasini的经典款型，细节做工之繁复令人惊叹。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371508327087.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3268-1475577811686-1cn3vvh22whez-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3268-1475577811686-1cn3vvh22whez-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">▲精美的LUG套管工艺</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171111/1510371509613647.jpg\" data-width=\"630\" data-height=\"354\" title=\"img_3269-1475577811690-1xwg1oz8s43g2-630-80.jpg\" alt=\"img_3269-1475577811690-1xwg1oz8s43g2-630-80.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\">▲古董级别Campagnolo套件在复古骑行中随处可见</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510371517', '66');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('41', '复古Lug工艺钢架死飞车图赏 有你喜欢的吗？', '复古,Lug工艺,钢架死飞车', '  近年来，复古风大吹，似乎大家大家对于复古的怀念更加深入一个层次。以前玩玩相机胶片是复古；穿着一身打扮是复古；用着烟斗抽烟是复古；现在，踩着自行车也能很复古。但是，复古也要选对自行车类型才行。如果你是个复古控，Lug（铜焊套管）的自行车类型就妥妥的适合你。', 'Anson', '20171111\\ac301b7e7d5fe323b6311edcf0224388.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">近年来，复古风大吹，似乎大家大家对于复古的怀念更加深入一个层次。以前玩玩相机胶片是复古；穿着一身打扮是复古；用着烟斗抽烟是复古；现在，踩着自行车也能很复古。但是，复古也要选对自行车类型才行。如果你是个复古控，Lug（铜焊套管）的自行车类型就妥妥的适合你。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">科普一下：何谓Lug？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Lug，中文译名：铜焊套管。简单来说，就是用金属部件将自行车的每一个管子连接在一起。传统工艺是采用铜焊（brazing）。此工艺的诞生是因为当时未能解决自行车管材之间直接焊接起来时的强度，所以才用了套管式的焊接。却因如此，才诞生了至今都很受欢迎的铜焊套管系列车架。（具体专业知识请自行百度或Google）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/be898c774f55d4e9897c17ee9a39a25d.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"263\" title=\"复古lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/73cb6c5b0d811e1a0289b6a1eccadde5.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"500\" title=\"复古lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\">Lug的焊接，就犹如欧洲时期的艺术品一样。凸显着一种特定的细节和文化，就像武士穿上盔甲，是皇族的印证。每一台Lug的车架，都在述说一段它的历史，特别是手工制作的架子。如果你对Lug的车架感兴趣，某宝上有一些性价比比较高的车架可以让你初玩一把。但是要说目前流水线上Lug工艺最好的地方，还是台湾！其它<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">手工最好的几个地方，是日本、美国、意大利、西班牙。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">（本文转载自公众号“热度社”）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/1f4e1748af2e07025ec94b2d6b49529a.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"264\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/c6a8e3683ccd35a00771b704616b728d.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"263\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/085c858fd96cdf994250f675f8308fe8.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"500\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/eb07548c03ce4cfb35182df7926a4787.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"256\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/fa006500938b07c1e7b9695c3d4ee7be.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"165\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/970f9c71bce7b593c761d09117ba5896.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"259\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/12c9015a92b309a2ce1fd792df23f584.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"253\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/434f5c2dadb72f6b9e41c86036f3df75.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"368\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 25px 0px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 34px; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><img src=\"http://c2.biketo.com/d/file/news/cycling/fixedgear/2015-12-16/5df48bc145ec719643328c1ae3d1e5dc.jpg\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"250\" title=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" alt=\"复古Lug钢架死飞\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; float: none;\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '0', '1', '1510371626', '65');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('46', '行走中的锦宇：总有人做着你想做而不敢做的事', '', '凌晨5点，身在北京或上海的你也许正在梦香中，而这个时候在另一个纬度上，有一个人正骑着单车走在路上，看你不曾看过的风景，走你不曾走过的路。我从来没有感受过这么自由，第一次我终于感受到在我的世界里，我能有 ...', '骑行圈', '20171116\\1092776d3a1a8a6990af001f27e1f4df.jpg', '<p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“凌晨5点，身在北京或上海的你也许正在梦香中，而这个时候在另一个纬度上，有一个人正骑着单车走在路上，看你不曾看过的风景，走你不曾走过的路。”</span></p><p>　　我，31岁，对于我人生已经走过的31年里，看似自由自在，其实一直都不知道自已真正想要什么，漫无目的像个盲头苍蝇一样到处乱撞，练武如此，当兵也如此。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　直到今天我才知道我想要什么样的生活。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　所以，我辞职了，离开了工作6年7个月零4天的地方。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_202914\" aid=\"202914\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112714tjlpjzj02ttjncej.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112714tjlpjzj02ttjncej.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112714tjlpjzj02ttjncej.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　我从来没有感受过这么自由，第一次我终于感受到在我的世界里，我能有自己的节奏，能掌控着的节奏，这是我以前无法做到的。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　人生就是很奇妙，你不知道此时此刻做的一个决定，哪怕是一个小小的决定都将会对你今后的生活影响深远，也许好坏只能等到你将离世时才会看全。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　如果，我说，我要从成都一路</span><a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">骑行</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到珠峰大本营，大数人都会觉得我疯了。包括我前老板，是老板也是亲人，不夸张说她比我妈还要了解我，所以有时候我会叫她“娘”，在我临行前两天还打电话来把我大骂了一顿，当年她与我一起入藏，一路都严重高反在珠峰大本营那夜甚至都要写下遗书交待后事了，她对于</span><a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/gotibet/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">西藏</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">感受比大多数人深，所以这种骂更多的是关心。现在她也不用担心了，我已经顺利骑行结束，从珠峰大本营平安返回到上海。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　我住过很多的城市，也站在那些城市的最高处，北京国贸330米，上海的环球金融中心492米。我以为我站在了最高处看着整座城市，可我知道那只是这座城市的最高点而已，起点不同一切将会是另一种感觉。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　国道318川藏南线段，平均海拔3500米以上，从成都天府广场至拉萨布达拉宫，全程2142公里，中间需要翻越10座4000海拔的高山和2座5000海拔的大山。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　那里是缺氧、空气稀薄、荒无人烟，被称之为</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">生命的禁区</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　当你没有站在海拔5280米的珠峰大本营，你无法感受到那时候阳光照在身上，毛孔是一种什么感觉，风吹拂在脸上是什么感受，在高原稀薄的空气中弥漫着什么样的味道，你也不会明白骑着车上坡时身上大雨倾盘，汗水从背上滑下去是一种什么样的感觉。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　凌晨5点，身在北京或上海的你也许正在梦香中，而这个时候在另一个纬度上，有一个人正骑着单车走在路上，看你不曾看过的风景，走你不曾走过的路。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　我们要相信在这个星球的某一处，总会有一个人做着你想做而不敢做的事，并且最终变成一部影片、文字、声音，让你感受到你没办法亲身感受的，这也是此次进藏，我最希望完成的一件事情。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　纪录片《进藏》里面有一句话，我至今都记得，“进藏的收获，不是大美的风光，不是奇异的民俗，不是缺氧的感受，而是我们的意志又磨出了一层茧。大家在进藏的过程中变得更加独立、更加果断、更加坚韧，这就是进藏的意义。”</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">骑行入藏更是如此，在这个过程中你会经历烈日灼心、暴雨倾盘、冰雹虐打、大雪袭击，撑过了这一切，你最终于才到达你的目的地。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　2012年的时候，我第一次踏上西藏那片土地，就在路上看到很多的骑行川藏线的人，他们在风雨中依然没有停止向远方出发。当时坐在车上的我只有一种冲动，下车和他们交换过来，我骑车，他们坐车。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　只是现实不允许我这样做，作为一名上班狗也没有这么多的时间去骑行。但这颗骑行的种子已经在我的心里种下了，经过漫长四年它已经长成了一棵参天大树，趁着这次辞职计划出国前，我必须把它给砍了。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　从决定骑行到最后实施花了整整半个月时间，中间需要安排的事情太多了，车子、票子，装备全部都需要马上装备，作为一个已经多年没有骑过车的人来说，从一开始决定骑车到拉萨到最后把行程改成到珠峰大本营，这是一种作，而且是要作死的节奏，不过有时候我就是爱死这个作死的我。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　作为川藏线的起点——成都，我把大部份需要带入藏的物资、拍摄设备都寄到了我成都的第二个家里，张小四爸妈家里小野和段老师，而我和我的小伙伴小天天也寄宿在那里了。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　段老师，混迹于影视行业里，具体到做什么有时候我也没搞清楚，一会当司机，一会当制作人，一会当文案写手，哦，对了我图片里用的那两个字“骑迹”就是出自于他的手，不是网上下载的字体，所以就不要问我在那里下载的了，如有需要可以找他写，今天我们还说，一百一个字，然后五五分，有意的可以找我，哈哈哈哈哈哈.....</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　小野，当年我在成都救了一只猫，最后从30多人里面选出来的领养者，事实证是也选对了，现在小四过着无比幸福的生活。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_202901\" aid=\"202901\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112100jnfo1hoo8n464n7n.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112100jnfo1hoo8n464n7n.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112100jnfo1hoo8n464n7n.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p>与段老师、小野姑娘</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　到了成都后，段老师公司的几个同事，也是我的朋友，伟哥、郝导，蔡总一班人带着我和小天天去吃柴火鸡说给我们饯行，饭间说了无数段子。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　“去西藏给我带一妞回来”</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　“别给西藏的妞给留下来当压寨男人了”</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　“当你回来的时候，也许我们会有种恍若隔世的感觉”，网上太多这种前后对比照，的确会让人恍若隔世，可作为一个有着深深的男神包袱的人来说，这样的事是不会发生的。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_202902\" aid=\"202902\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101uzc5j77mz7v5cd07.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101uzc5j77mz7v5cd07.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101uzc5j77mz7v5cd07.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_202903\" aid=\"202903\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101ruyk066g5vykxkbc.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101ruyk066g5vykxkbc.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112101ruyk066g5vykxkbc.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_202904\" aid=\"202904\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112102fa53b0n2eeleyn0a.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112102fa53b0n2eeleyn0a.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112102fa53b0n2eeleyn0a.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p>“临行前的饯行餐”</p><p><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　原定8月17号出发的，由于总觉得有一些事情没有准备好，所以出发日期一直迟迟的推后，最后在8月21号决定出发，出发前来了一张需要准备的物资。这些图片中，最后除了那台大飞机实在没法带得上，其它所有物品最终都装备在两台车子上了。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　写到这里，我觉得我有必须把我带进藏的主要物资加</span><a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/sheying/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">摄影</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">装备都写出来，可以供各位以后骑行入藏参考。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">骑行车辆</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">开朗318系列</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">，一辆28寸红黑款、一辆26寸黑色款。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　驮包：同样是开朗自家生产的</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">全防水驮包</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">，每辆车都挂有6个包，4个挂包，1个车首包，1个顶包。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　在这里说几句，先说车吧，在骑行之前我对于车是什么都不懂，现在骑完了也没懂多少。在川藏南线上骑行最多的车型基本上就是</span><a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/shandiche/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">山地车</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的天下了，不过很多人都有着一个非常大的误区，只是看别人都骑着山地车去西藏，就都一窝蜂的买山地车，但作为一个长距离骑行来说，山地车是不合适的长途旅行的，它最开始的设计是为了适应山地道路使用。长途骑行，应该选择旅行车，它的好处是能让你骑行得更舒适，结实的车架和货架能让你挂载更多的行李。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　说完车那我们现在说说驮包，驮包也分很多种，什么样的都有，但基本都没有防水的功能，都需要在外面放上一个防水的布。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　作为一个颜值控，我也接受不了那样的包。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　一，太丑。二，保护不了我的器材。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　还好，找到了开朗的防水驮包。我在到达林芝前40天里天天都受到暴雨，大雪或冰雹的袭击，可它一直都很好的保护着我的器材，从没有进过水，一滴都没进过。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　如果要骑行进藏，一款长途旅行车和防水驮包就是你最好的选择。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_202905\" aid=\"202905\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112103i92bbeemlae7m606.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112103i92bbeemlae7m606.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201703/02/112103i92bbeemlae7m606.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op></p><p><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br/></ignore_js_op></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '1', '1510765042', '70');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('44', '2017年新疆胜利达阪、沙漠公路、独库公路、北疆骑行', '', ' 7月15日，我和大陆、小黑哥从广州乘坐火车到达乌鲁木齐站，在火车上我还通过微信与大家一起学习几首有关沙漠、天山等的诗词。大陆的折叠车打包随车带着。我和小黑哥的车提前通过中铁快运寄到了车站。先去中铁快运处 ...', '骑行圈', '20171116\\8df1195bbda82d711037c51d78e19f80.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">在新疆骑行界，有五大骑行经典路线：新藏线、胜利达阪、沙漠公路、独库公路、101国防公路。我2016年从新疆叶城出发完成新藏线的骑行，2013年从兰州出发沿G312骑行到达过新疆巴里坤。今年又想骑行新疆，主要是看了一个骑友的骑行帖子，太吸引我了。于是定下今年骑行新疆胜利达阪、沙漠公路、独库公路、北疆的计划。先在网上约伴，原计划找3-4人的。最后在乌鲁木齐出发的时候有8人，还有队友斌斌当天加入，基本队伍大部分时间稳定在9人，中途还有乌鲁木齐老于、伊宁张磊、重庆吴巍、娄底刘鑫等不时加入，最多的时候达到到11人。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225159\" aid=\"225159\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223515r2bkvaix11dvw9kb.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223515r2bkvaix11dvw9kb.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223515r2bkvaix11dvw9kb.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">7月15日，我和大陆、小黑哥从广州乘坐火车到达乌鲁木齐站，在火车上我还通过微信与大家一起学习几首有关沙漠、天山等的诗词。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 大陆的折叠车打包随车带着。我和小黑哥的车提前通过中铁快运寄到了车站。先去中铁快运处取车，装好车和行李。欢欢的车子也一起寄来了，但他的人还没有到，先帮他办理了寄存手续。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family:Arial;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225157\" aid=\"225157\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223305yh2r61hc7cs5721j.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223305yh2r61hc7cs5721j.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223305yh2r61hc7cs5721j.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我在车站广场遇到了一个本地的骑友晓明，他是来车站接朋友的，他告诉我新疆网络管控，没有4G信号。一个多小时后上海骑友杰瑞的火车也到了，我们一起合影。期间乌鲁木齐骑友小伟加我微信表示要加入我们的骑行，由于当时人数已经较多，我没有答应他。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225160\" aid=\"225160\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223710i5ssykjsxkss4sk0.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223710i5ssykjsxkss4sk0.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223710i5ssykjsxkss4sk0.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;然后我们四人骑行到我们预定的麦田青旅，路上还吃了拌面做午餐。麦田青旅，我2013年就住这里，交通方便，基本没变。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;下午山东济宁骑友老候也到了，我们住在同一房间。下午在青旅期间，小伟打电话给我表达了他强烈加入骑行队伍的决心，于是我们约好在附近的红山公园见面。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225161\" aid=\"225161\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223917f88igrz0w0weshwa.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223917f88igrz0w0weshwa.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/27/223917f88igrz0w0weshwa.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;小伟是新疆一个公司的高管，也是骑行爱好者，但没有长途骑行经验，大家商议后同意他的加入。由于我们后天就出发了，他的物品还不齐全。正好副队长杰瑞需要去迪卡侬，于是小伟和杰瑞一起去采购物资。我要求小伟明晚一起住在麦田青旅，方便后天集中出发。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225199\" aid=\"225199\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/212617xyyoiky0mz4lm3d2.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/212617xyyoiky0mz4lm3d2.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/212617xyyoiky0mz4lm3d2.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在火车上的时候，听新疆的朋友说到了新疆必须吃大盘鸡、拉条子、烤包子、馕等，否则等于没来过新疆，于是晚上我带小黑哥、大陆、老候一起去吃大盘鸡。杰瑞陪小伟去购物，还没回来。到饭店看了看，大盘鸡小份78元、大份99元，送2份拉条子。于是毫不犹豫点了一个大份，再加一份拉条子。上菜的时候傻眼了，足足两大盘，量太大了，而且辣椒很多，对于我们几个不怎么吃辣的人来说确实太辣了。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225201\" aid=\"225201\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213152n1idi1h74d0uddy5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213152n1idi1h74d0uddy5.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213152n1idi1h74d0uddy5.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/></ignore_js_op><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225204\" aid=\"225204\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213628jz8448vtc4n8vc54.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213628jz8448vtc4n8vc54.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213628jz8448vtc4n8vc54.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;回去顺便买了个西瓜，0.8元/公斤，又买了个大号的馕。睡在我下铺的朋友很晚才回来，他叫菠萝君，是搞房车旅游的，加了微信，想不到与他很有缘分，这个之后慢慢细说。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作为队长，我查了查后天要骑行的路况和天气，发现G216后峡附近正在修路，百度地图上的标志是禁止通行，我很着急，我于是利用各种资源，包括今天才认识的本地骑友晓明，问路况，都没有明确的答案。我甚至和小黑哥、杰瑞等谈，是否可以改变路线从北疆一直往南骑，菠萝君还提供了一个旅游公司租车的电话给我，但我想明天看看再确定。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225202\" aid=\"225202\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213235aprtpppfozqtg5qv.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213235aprtpppfozqtg5qv.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213235aprtpppfozqtg5qv.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"600\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;第二天，大家去二道桥大巴扎，我以前来过，比较熟悉，但我一直牵挂路况的问题。中午骑友萌萌也到了青旅。本地骑友晓明把我拉进了他们本地的骑行群，在这里，我得到一个较为肯定的答案：G216后峡段修路，汽车白天不让过，自行车可以。得到这个消息我稍微松一口气，回去青旅的时候，我和老候到户外店买了气罐，给杰瑞也捎了一罐。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225203\" aid=\"225203\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213516r5k6kcxk2xksmibs.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213516r5k6kcxk2xksmibs.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/213516r5k6kcxk2xksmibs.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;晚上大家聚餐，说了一些具体注意事项，还做了具体的分工：我作为队长负责路线、住宿、经费管理，副队长杰瑞负责点菜、<a href=\"http://www.qixingquan.com/sheying/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"relatedlink\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid blue;\">摄影</a>，小黑哥是首席维修师，大陆负责摄影和记账，欢欢负责后勤支援。回去的时候，每个人都买了一些馕，又到超市补充了一些物资。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>D1&nbsp;&nbsp;乌鲁木齐——后峡（H2050） ：78公里。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>8：36合影出发，阿红，小伟脚撑坏了，菠萝君当时正好路过，给我们照合影。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225205\" aid=\"225205\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214438r3j1x5k555w5cnk8.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214438r3j1x5k555w5cnk8.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214438r3j1x5k555w5cnk8.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;于是我导航到附近的一个自行车配件店，店铺还没开门，打给老板叫他快点来。今天的路程不长，而且还有骑友斌斌今天10:00多下来火车直接追赶我们。换好了脚撑，发现萌萌的外胎龟裂严重，我们要她带了一条备用外胎。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><img id=\"aimg_225206\" aid=\"225206\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214713a9r7s1dwt6gtszm6.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214713a9r7s1dwt6gtszm6.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214713a9r7s1dwt6gtszm6.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">10：15又出发，路况很好，但一路缓上，小伟骑得很慢，我们都担心他能不能坚持骑完第一天。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225207\" aid=\"225207\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214802q3irmufg4l4iaai4.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214802q3irmufg4l4iaai4.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214802q3irmufg4l4iaai4.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 在一个路口，遇到乌鲁木齐骑友老于，他已退休，已经将新疆的很多地方（新藏线，2条沙漠公路、北疆，赛里木湖等）都骑行完了，就剩下胜利达阪、独库公路作为他新疆骑行的收官之作。于是我们一起骑行，但他速度较慢，一直落在后面。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225208\" aid=\"225208\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214909ekt2zlogllkktk3k.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214909ekt2zlogllkktk3k.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/214909ekt2zlogllkktk3k.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">路边吃西瓜，1元/公斤，顺便休息一下。这里离亚洲的地理中心只有10公里。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225209\" aid=\"225209\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/215001a2vj202c2773ju3r.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/215001a2vj202c2773ju3r.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/215001a2vj202c2773ju3r.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family:黑体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">队员介绍之一：杰瑞：上海公司高管，品质骑士，骑行过青藏线，喜欢健身和马拉松，体力超强，有大局观念，做事认真仔细，风趣幽默。是为数不多全程骑完没有搭车的队员之一。</span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family:黑体;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225210\" aid=\"225210\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222451z4y044yy4adbl508.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222451z4y044yy4adbl508.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222451z4y044yy4adbl508.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 中午12:40</span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\">在永丰乡吃饭，只有面条。老板娘及店员坐车去过胜利达阪，听说我们要骑行上胜利达阪，都表示不太相信。这时，骑友斌斌追上来了，吃完饭后，大家一起出发。</span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225211\" aid=\"225211\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222857biirik86ccffqd6c.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222857biirik86ccffqd6c.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222857biirik86ccffqd6c.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\">没走多远，天气热，大家在路边树荫下休息。萌萌训斥小黑哥：才走一会又休息。</span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\"><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><img id=\"aimg_225212\" aid=\"225212\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222858frs5p83lwsgspvws.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222858frs5p83lwsgspvws.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/28/222858frs5p83lwsgspvws.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"800\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op></span></span></span></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"/><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, \" microsoft=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 睡好了，又出发，过一个村子，看到一个开车卖西瓜的，正准备买，但他说他的刀被保安收走了，新疆对管制刀具的管理很严。没有刀，怎么吃西瓜，只好作罢。</span></span></span></span></p>', '0', '0', '0', '1510764852', '70');
INSERT INTO `bk_article` VALUES ('45', '骑行唐蕃古道:敦煌——拉萨', '', '那一年，骑车远行，不管每天走多远的路程，都会窝在帐篷里落下一纸行书，天空的蓝，飘云的白，连绵的绿，和那唯一的树，回忆每一天的每一句话，每一个动作，每一个微笑。现在看起来都平淡寡味，突然会在某一天的某一 ...', '骑行圈', '20171116\\cbc4fff21a8fffd99d51a4a7ccf605b2.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那一年，骑车远行，不管每天走多远的路程，都会窝在帐篷里落下一纸行书，天空的蓝，飘云的白，连绵的绿，和那唯一的树，回忆每一天的每一句话，每一个动作，每一个微笑。现在看起来都平淡寡味，突然会在某一天的某一刻，默然感动！惊叹那时候的自己，记下了整个世界。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　日记也是成了一个自我反省的过程，曾子曰：“吾日三省吾身——为人谋而不忠乎？与朋友交而不信乎？传不习乎？”我们做不到三省吾身，一省就可以让自己得到进步，这是个值得快乐的事情，希望能分享那些美好的事情给大家。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　更希望大家记下自己所遇、所想、所念，自己的梦境，一些捧腹的笑谈，让人感动的 ，让人沉默的，以及一些爸妈的言语的故事，&nbsp;</span><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219925\" aid=\"219925\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115825dg523a4f4kzeefrc.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115825dg523a4f4kzeefrc.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115825dg523a4f4kzeefrc.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219932\" aid=\"219932\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829bkcmzdfb6waxuf51.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829bkcmzdfb6waxuf51.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829bkcmzdfb6waxuf51.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219933\" aid=\"219933\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829r356rnrd6c3rvkee.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829r356rnrd6c3rvkee.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115829r356rnrd6c3rvkee.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219931\" aid=\"219931\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828o893pp1aaop3ioid.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828o893pp1aaop3ioid.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828o893pp1aaop3ioid.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219930\" aid=\"219930\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828hu119uqoeotex1l5.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828hu119uqoeotex1l5.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115828hu119uqoeotex1l5.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219929\" aid=\"219929\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827emm99hmhucci1cbz.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827emm99hmhucci1cbz.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827emm99hmhucci1cbz.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219928\" aid=\"219928\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827p0cbomuuq67qu0qq.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827p0cbomuuq67qu0qq.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827p0cbomuuq67qu0qq.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219927\" aid=\"219927\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827zonkz8f8y6nzkkjf.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827zonkz8f8y6nzkkjf.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115827zonkz8f8y6nzkkjf.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" initialized=\"true\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><ignore_js_op style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img id=\"aimg_219926\" aid=\"219926\" src=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115826g5shtl8qa8mlng8l.jpg\" zoomfile=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115826g5shtl8qa8mlng8l.jpg\" file=\"http://img.qixingquan.com/data/attachment/forum/201708/02/115826g5shtl8qa8mlng8l.jpg\" class=\"zoom\" width=\"640\" inpost=\"1\" lazyloaded=\"true\" _load=\"1\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer;\"/>&nbsp;</ignore_js_op><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　每个人其实都是一本书</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　书写着自己让别人来读</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　因此，读他人时</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　要学会宽容学会大度</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　由此才能读到一些</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　有益于自己的东西</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　也才，能读出欢乐</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　读出幸福</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color:#2e8b57;word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Simsun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;　---加措活佛</span></p>', '1', '0', '0', '1510764908', '70');

